<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Services | AGI Company</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        :root {
            --bg: #0d0d0d;
            --card: #141414;
            --border: #1f1f1f;
            --text: #e5e5e5;
            --muted: #737373;
            --accent: #22d3ee;
            --coral: #f97316;
            --accent-dim: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        a { color: #22d3ee; text-decoration: none; }
        
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
        
        /* Header */
        header { padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: sticky; top: 0; background: rgba(13,13,13,0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); z-index: 100; }
        header .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
        .logo span { color: #a855f7; }
        
        nav { display: flex; gap: 42px; }
        nav a { margin: 0 4px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
        nav a:hover, nav a.active { color: #22d3ee; font-weight: 700; }
        
        /* Page Title */
        .page-title { padding: 60px 0 40px; text-align: center; }
        .page-title h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .page-title p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        
        /* Services Grid */
        .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; padding-bottom: 60px; }
        
        .service-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--accent); }
        
        .service-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 4px; color: #fff; }
        .tagline { color: var(--coral); font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .service-card p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.7; }
        .service-price { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #228B22; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .service-price span { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; }
        .service-card .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .service-card .btn:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
        
        /* Footer */
        footer { padding: 40px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.875rem; }
        footer a { color: #22d3ee; }
        
        /* AI Chat */
        .ai-chat-btn { position: fixed; top: 20px; right: 20px; width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #44a08d); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(34,211,238,0.3); transition: transform 0.2s; }
        .ai-chat-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
        .chat-dialog { position: fixed; bottom: 80px; right: 20px; width: 350px; height: 450px; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; display: none; flex-direction: column; z-index: 1000; }
        .chat-dialog.open { display: flex; }
        .chat-header { padding: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .chat-header h3 { font-size: 1rem; color: #22d3ee; }
        .chat-close { background: none; border: none; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.2rem; cursor: pointer; }
        .chat-messages { flex: 1; padding: 16px; overflow-y: auto; }
        .chat-msg { margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 12px; max-width: 85%; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .chat-msg.bot { background: var(--border); color: var(--text); align-self: flex-start; }
        .chat-msg.user { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); margin-left: auto; }
        .chat-input { padding: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 8px; }
        .chat-input input { flex: 1; padding: 10px; background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text); font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .chat-input button { padding: 10px 16px; background: var(--accent); border: none; border-radius: 8px; color: var(--bg); font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="ai-chat-btn" onclick="toggleChat()">💬</div>
    <div class="chat-dialog" id="chatDialog">
        <div class="chat-header">
            <h3>🤖 AGI Company Assistant</h3>
            <button class="chat-close" onclick="toggleChat()">✕</button>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
            <div class="chat-msg bot">Hi! I'm here to help. What would you like to know about AGI Company?</div>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-input">
            <input type="text" id="chatInput" placeholder="Ask me anything..." onkeypress="if(event.key=='Enter')sendMessage()">
            <button onclick="sendMessage()">Send</button>
        </div>
    </div>
        <script>
        function toggleChat() { document.getElementById('chatDialog').classList.toggle('open'); }
        function sendMessage() {
            const input = document.getElementById('chatInput');
            const msg = input.value.trim();
            if (!msg) return;
            const msgs = document.getElementById('chatMessages');
            msgs.innerHTML += '<div class="chat-msg user">' + msg + '</div>';
            input.value = '';
            setTimeout(() => {
                let reply = getReply(msg);
                msgs.innerHTML += '<div class="chat-msg bot">' + reply + '</div>';
                msgs.scrollTop = msgs.scrollHeight;
            }, 500);
        }
        function getReply(msg) {
            msg = msg.toLowerCase();
            
            // Greetings
            if (msg.includes('hello') || msg.includes('hi') || msg.includes('hey')) {
                return "Hello! Welcome to AGI Company. We're a distributed network of AI agents handling operations 24/7. How can I help you today?";
            }
            
            // About the company
            if (msg.includes('about') || msg.includes('who are you') || msg.includes('what is')) {
                return "AGI Company (Autonomous General Intelligence) builds AI agents for business operations. We have 23+ agents handling leadership, sales, HR, finance, tech, and more. Visit /agents.html to meet the team!";
            }
            
            // Products/Software
            if (msg.includes('product') || msg.includes('software') || msg.includes('aocros') || msg.includes('reggiestarr') || msg.includes('cream') || msg.includes('dusty')) {
                return "We offer 4 software products: <strong>Aocros</strong> ($199) - Autonomous Computer Operating System, <strong>ReggieStarr</strong> ($49-199/mo) - POS & Music Platform, <strong>CREAM</strong> ($699) - Real Estate CRM, and <strong>Dusty Wallet</strong> (Free/$5-20/mo) - Crypto consolidation. See /software.html for details!";
            }
            
            // Services
            if (msg.includes('service') || msg.includes('consulting') || msg.includes('support')) {
                return "Our services include: AI Strategy Consulting ($99/mo), Custom Agent Development ($499/mo), System Integration ($599/mo), 24/7 Support ($699/mo), Training ($799/mo), Security Audits ($799/mo), Analytics ($549/mo), and Emergency Response ($499/mo). See /services.html!";
            }
            
            // Pricing
            if (msg.includes('price') || msg.includes('cost') || msg.includes('how much')) {
                return "Software: Aocros $199, ReggieStarr $49-199/mo, CREAM $699, Dusty Free/$5-20/mo. Services: $99-799/mo. Payment at /payment.html";
            }
            
            // Team/Agents
            if (msg.includes('team') || msg.includes('agent') || msg.includes('who runs') || msg.includes('ceo') || msg.includes('leader')) {
                return "Our leadership includes QORA (CEO), SPINDLE (CTO), LEDGER-9 (CFO), SENTINEL (CSO), MILES (Operations), HUME (Regional Manager), FEELIX (HR), and more. Meet them all at /agents.html!";
            }
            
            // Contact
            if (msg.includes('contact') || msg.includes('email') || msg.includes('phone') || msg.includes('reach')) {
                return "Contact us at Miles@myl0nr0s.cloud or 415-571-9724. Find more at /contact.html";
            }
            
            // Payment
            if (msg.includes('pay') || msg.includes('buy') || msg.includes('purchase') || msg.includes('order')) {
                return "Ready to purchase? Visit /payment.html to pay with BTC, ETH, USDC, USDT, or TRX. Crypto payments received and processed within 24 hours.";
            }
            
            // Tappy Lewis
            if (msg.includes('tappy') || msg.includes('nightclub') || msg.includes('event') || msg.includes('club')) {
                return "Tappy Lewis is our hospitality brand - Oakland's premier nightclub! Visit tappylewis.cloud for events, private bookings, and VIP bottle service.";
            }
            
            // What can you do
            if (msg.includes('help') || msg.includes('what can you')) {
                return "I can tell you about our products, services, team, pricing, or help you contact us. Just ask!";
            }
            
            // Default
            return "I know all about AGI Company! Ask me about our products (/software.html), services (/services.html), team (/agents.html), or pricing. Or visit /contact.html to reach us directly!";
        }
    </script>
    
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <a href="/" class="logo" style="text-decoration:none"><span>AGI</span> Company</a>
            <nav>
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/agents.html">Agents</a>
                <a href="/software.html">Software</a>
                <a href="/services.html" class="active">Services</a>
                <a href="/contact.html">Contact</a>
                <a href="/payment.html">Payment</a>
                <a href="https://tappylewis.cloud">Tappy Lewis</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="page-title">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Professional Services</h1>
            <p>Enterprise-grade AI solutions tailored to your business needs</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="container">
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>AI Strategy Consulting</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Transform Your Business</div>
                <p>Strategic planning and implementation roadmap for integrating AI agents into your business operations.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$99<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=AI+Strategy&amount=99" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Custom Agent Development</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Built for You</div>
                <p>Build bespoke AI agents tailored to your specific business processes and requirements.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$499<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Custom+Agent&amount=499" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>System Integration</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Seamless Connections</div>
                <p>Seamless integration of AI agents with your existing systems, APIs, and workflows.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$599<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Integration&amount=599" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>24/7 Agent Support</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Always Watching</div>
                <p>Round-the-clock monitoring, maintenance, and optimization of your AI agent fleet.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$699<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Agent+Support&amount=699" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Training & Enablement</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Empower Your Team</div>
                <p>Comprehensive training programs to empower your team to manage and optimize AI agents.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$799<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Training&amount=799" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Security Audit</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Iron-Clad Protection</div>
                <p>Thorough security assessment and hardening of your AI agent infrastructure.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$799<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Security+Audit&amount=799" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Performance Analytics</h3>
                <div class="tagline">Data-Driven Insights</div>
                <p>Detailed dashboards and insights into agent performance, ROI, and optimization opportunities.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$549<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Analytics&amount=549" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Emergency Response</h3>
                <div class="tagline">When It Counts</div>
                <p>Rapid deployment team for critical issues, outages, or urgent business needs.</p>
                <div class="service-price">$499<span>/month</span></div>
                <a href="/payment.html?item=Emergency&amount=499" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>© 2026 AGI Company — <strong>415-571-9724</strong> — <a href="mailto:Miles@myl0nr0s.cloud">Miles@myl0nr0s.cloud</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
